<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEIGHBORHOOD EATERY: MORE EATERIES: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN WEYLER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Donut World, 34852 Doheny Park Road, Capistrano Beach. Open Mondays through 
Saturdays 5 a.m. to 5 p.m., Sundays till 3 p.m. (714) 496-2454. 
</P>
<P>
There are nearly two dozen varieties available, but most who come here order a 
doughnut only as an afterthought. Breakfast sandwiches are a hot item, as are 
massive breakfast plates with four strips of bacon. Or drop by at lunch, when 
the cheeseburger special comes with a choice of fries or egg roll. JOHN WEYLER 
</P>
