<HEADLINE>
<P>
NEIGHBORHOOD EATERY: MORE EATERIES: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By APRIL JACKSON 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Salerno, 220 Beach St., Laguna Beach. Open 11:30 a.m. to 10 p.m. Wednesdays 
through Mondays. (714) 497-2600. 
</P>
<P>
Owner Tony Manzi's accent is nearly as thick as his meat sauce, and his menu is 
just as hearty. Try the gnocchi, baked mostaccoli with Italian sausage or, if 
you happen to be dining with understanding friends, the fettuccini with garlic 
and oil. APRIL JACKSON 
</P>
