THE CORNER BAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By ROBYN NORWOOD 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MORE BARS: 
</P>
<P>
The Place (Mike's Sports Bar), 2920 E. Coast Highway, Corona del Mar. 
</P>
<P>
Open daily, 10 a.m. to midnight. (714) 644-0210. Three satellite dishes, seven 
small TV screens, sports memorabilia on the walls and famous athletes dropping 
by for a visit. Make no mistake, this is an all-sports bar. ROBYN NORWOOD 
</P>
