RELATIONS -- IRAQ; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES -- PERSIAN GULF; MILITARY 
STRATEGY; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN POLICY; OIL PRICES; OIL INDUSTRY -- SAUDI 
