Bd2/Qxb2; 22. Bxb4/Bf7; 23. Re6/Qxb4; 24. Rb3/Qxa4; 25. Bc2/Rad8; 26. Rbe3/Qb4; 
27. g3/a5; 28. Nh4/d5; 29. Qe2/Qc4; 30. Bd3/Qc1ch; 
</P>
<P>
31. Kg2/c4; 32. Bc2/Bxe6; 33. Rxe6/Rxe6; 34. Qxe6ch/Kh8; 35. Ng6ch/Kh7; 36. 
Qe2/Qg5; 37. f6/Qxf6; 38. Nxf8ch/Kg8; 39. Ng6/Qf7; 40. Ne7ch/Kf8; 41. Move 
sealed by white. Game adjourned. 
