The right blend?; Photo, D'Oyly Carte Administrative Manager Ian Martin and 
chairman Bishop: would-be guardians of tradition. BOB WORKMAN / For the Times; 
Photo, Under the makeup, a younger look. DEBORA ROBINSON / For The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
