<P>
WESTSIDE DIGEST: WEST HOLLYWOOD; 
</P>
<P>
5K-10K RUN PLANNED 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
West Hollywood's sixth annual Tom Proctor 5K-10K Run and Walkathon will be held 
at 8 a.m. Oct. 28 at West Hollywood Park, 647 N. San Vicente Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
The Tom Proctor Run and Walkathon is part of the city's Halloween Week 
celebration that will include a costume competition. Music, games, a free 
drawing and a diaper dash will also be featured. 
</P>
<P>
Proceeds from the race and pledges by individuals will benefit Pets Are 
Wonderful Support/Los Angeles (Paws/LA). PAWS is a nonprofit organization that 
helps people with AIDS care for their pets. For information on the Tom Proctor 
run, call (213) 854-7471. 
